25|$|There {{are often}} several regions of {{reflector}} voltage where the <b>reflex</b> <b>klystron</b> will oscillate; these {{are referred to}} as modes. The electronic tuning range of the <b>reflex</b> <b>klystron</b> is usually referred to as the variation in frequency between half power pointsthe points in the oscillating mode where the power output is half the maximum output in the mode.|$|E
