50|$|Most Devyatkov's {{scientific}} papers {{apply to}} a microwave vacuum tubes. He was an {{author of more than}} 250 scientific works and inventions. Nikolay Devyatkov is inventor of a <b>reflex</b> <b>klystron</b> (1939, with E. Daniltcev).|$|E
